    "updated_at": "2025-02-12T17:25:50Z",
    "body": "This is already possible with [conditional format strings](https://starship.rs/config/#conditional-format-strings) since they work across multiple lines:\n\n```toml\nformat = \"\"\"\n$directory\\\n(\\\n[ > ](fg:color_aqua)\\\n$git_branch\\\n$git_status\\\n)\\\n$line_break$character\"\"\"\n```\n\nIn this case, if all of the variables inside the section are empty, the rest of the content inside the open/close parentheses will not show:\n\n```\n~/projects/somegitrepo > main [!]\n$ cd ..\n~/projects\n$ \n```",
